# Research Project Management

## Build Phase Workflow
- Use tasks to manage research activities.
- Track tasks in `/docs/tasks.md`.
- Follow `/docs/literature-review.md` and `/docs/methodology.md`.

## Task Management
- Create new tasks in `/docs/tasks/` using a simple task template.
- Update `/docs/tasks.md` with task statuses.
- Confirm task completion with the user.